      "description": "# ğŸ¨ Custom Attributes\n\nThese custom profile attributes are like the car setup data for each team:\n\n- **team_color**: Each team's signature color scheme\n- **team_principal**: The team boss (like Toto Wolff or Christian Horner)\n- **home_circuit**: Their favorite track\n- **specialty**: What they're known for (aerodynamics, engine power, etc.)\n\nThis metadata helps us organize and understand our teams beyond just names!"
